  {
    "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/temporary/d6ac400e-2891-4aac-a156-9342a60ab0e6",
    "@type": [
      "http://schema.org/Event"
    ],
    "http://schema.org/mainEntityOfPage": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/spectacles/jules-et-josephine/"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/image": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/genid/f02c959e9e4a6e03"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/spectacles/jules-et-josephine/"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/startDate": [
      {
        "@type": "http://schema.org/Date",
        "@value": "2026-11-15T14:00:00-04:00"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/location": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/genid/17b0bf9e8c2a07c8"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/keywords": [
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Jeune public"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Théâtre"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/genid/34432a9fe75a2494"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/performer": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/genid/4fcba932d69234d1"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/organizer": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/#identity"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://co-motion.ca/spectacles/jules-et-josephine/"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "<p><sup><a href=\"https://www.theatreaqp.ca/jules-josephine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Théâtre Advienne Que Pourra</a><br />Durée : 60 minutes</sup></p>\n<p>Férue de science, Joséphine Verne correspond avidement de son Québec natal avec son cousin français Jules. Entre leurs rêves de voyages ou de fiction, une pensée commune les habite : « Il y a en moi des mondes que je ne soupçonne pas. »</p>\n<p>Pour provoquer enfin leur rencontre, Joséphine lui parie 80 livres qu’elle traversera l’Atlantique d’ici à la prochaine lune. Du Saint-Laurent jusqu’à La Loire, les personnages auront tout ce qu’il faut pour entrer dans l’histoire, celle avec un grand J.</p>\n<p>Profitez de votre venue pour visiter les expositions de <a href=\"https://www.laval.ca/culture/maison-des-arts/expositions-salle-alfred-pellan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">l’Espace muséal Alfred-Pellan.</a><br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.laval.ca/diffusart\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button btn-primary\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Diffusart</a></p>"
      }
    ],
